```
This is trivial. Now we need to compute the variance.
The variance of `Ōłæ k, L_k X_k` is `Ōłæ k, Ōłæ l, L_k L_l Cov(X_k, X_l)`.
This is exactly `Ōłæ i j, L_i L_j C_{i,j}`.
```tactics
